    "description": "Peers Co.,Ltd. provides consulting solutions. provides consulting services offers three main services: sales promotion, online customer service, and AI boarding. The company supports digital transformation to achieve labor-saving and automation in store operations, provides online customer service systems to stores, and offers comprehensive human resource development support services in the sales field. It offers Onlinx, an online customer service system; video call center systems; Mimik, a training AI system to analyze facial expressions and emotions; online customer service center management; and RemoteworkBOX, a service to reserve a private booth in the city with a smartphone. The company also provides education training; consulting services; sales promotion services, such as in-store events and operational improvements at sales sites; and professional personnel staffing services. Peers Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
